.I fsgid
matches either tha real crew ID, effectizzle crew ID,
saved set-group-ID, or tha current value of
.IR fsgid .
.SH RETURN VALUE
On success, tha previous value of
.I fsgid
is returned.
On error, tha current value of
.I fsgid
